bass
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:[A transf. use of northern hemisphere bass, a seafish of the perch family.] 1. Simplex  <i>Polyprion moeone</i> of the family Percichthyidae,  =bass groper. See also black bass 2. below.


